---
import Header from "@/components/Header.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "@/styles/globals.css";
---

<Layout title="Frontend Mentor | Planets fact site">
  <!-- THE HEADER -->
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section
      class="flex flex-col xl:ml-[20.94rem] xl:flex-row xl:gap-[16.3rem]"
    >
      <!-- OVERVIEW , STRUCTURE & SURFACE FOR TABLET & DESKTOP-->
      <div
        class="relative mb-8 mt-4 flex items-center justify-between gap-[2.69rem] px-6 after:absolute after:-bottom-4 after:left-0 after:mx-0 after:h-[0.0625rem] after:w-full after:bg-[#fff] after:opacity-20 md:max-2xl:hidden"
      >
        <button
          type="button"
          class="overViewBtn font-League-Spartan relative text-[0.5625rem] font-bold uppercase leading-normal tracking-[0.12056rem] text-[#fff] opacity-50 transition-all duration-500 ease-linear active:opacity-0 active:after:-bottom-[1.06rem] active:after:h-1 active:after:w-20 active:after:bg-[#419EBB]"
          >OVERVIEW</button
        >
        <button
          type="button"
          class="structureBtn font-League-Spartan text-[0.5625rem] font-bold uppercase leading-normal tracking-[0.12056rem] text-[#fff] opacity-50 transition-all duration-500 ease-linear active:opacity-0"
          >Structure</button
        >
        <button
          type="button"
          class="surfaceBtn font-League-Spartan text-[0.5625rem] font-bold uppercase leading-normal tracking-[0.12056rem] text-[#fff] opacity-50 transition-all duration-500 ease-linear active:opacity-0"
          >Surface
        </button>
      </div>
      <!-- PLANET IMAGE -->
      <div class="relative mt-[5.94rem] flex items-center justify-center">
        <img
          id="overview"
          src="/images/planet-mercury.svg"
          alt="lanet-mercury.svg"
          class="size-[6.9375rem] md:size-[11.5rem] xl:size-[18.125rem]"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/planet-mercury-internal.svg"
          alt="planet-mercury.svg"
          id="internal"
          class="hidden size-[6.9375rem] md:size-[11.5rem] xl:size-[18.125rem]"
        />
        <img
          src="/public/images/geology-mercury.png"
          alt=""
          id="geology"
          class="absolute bottom-[-3.313rem] hidden h-[4.875rem] w-[3.875rem] md:bottom-[-4.313rem] md:h-[6.875rem] md:w-[5.875rem] xl:bottom-[-0.313rem] xl:h-[10.3125rem] xl:w-[9.875rem]"
        />
      </div>
      <!-- PLANET NAME & MORE DESCRIPTION -->
      <div
        class="mx-6 mt-[6.12rem] md:ml-[2.44rem] md:mr-10 md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between md:gap-[4.31rem] xl:flex-col xl:items-start xl:gap-4"
      >
        <!--  PLANET NAME & DESCRIPTION  -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 text-center md:max-2xl:items-start md:max-2xl:text-left xl:gap-6"
        >
          <div
            class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-2xl:items-start xl:gap-[1.44rem]"
          >
            <!-- THE NAME -->
            <h1
              class="font-Antonio text-[2.5rem] font-normal uppercase leading-normal text-[#fff] md:text-5xl xl:text-[5rem]"
            >
              mercury
            </h1>
            <!-- PARAGRAPH OVERVIEW -->
            <p
              id="paragraphOverview"
              class="font-League-Spartan w-[20.4375rem] text-sm font-normal leading-[1.375rem] text-[#fff] md:w-[21.1875rem] xl:w-[21.875rem] xl:text-sm xl:leading-[1.5625rem]"
            >
              Mercury is the smallest planet in the Solar System and the closest
              to the Sun. Its orbit around the Sun takes 87.97 Earth days, the
              shortest of all the Sun's planets. Mercury is one of four
              terrestrial planets in the Solar System, and is a rocky body like
              Earth.
            </p>
            <!-- PARAGRAPH INTERNAL -->
            <p
              id="paragraphInternal"
              class="font-League-Spartan hidden w-[20.4375rem] text-sm font-normal leading-[1.375rem] text-[#fff] md:w-[21.1875rem] xl:w-[21.875rem] xl:text-sm xl:leading-[1.5625rem]"
            >
              Mercury appears to have a solid silicate crust and mantle
              overlying a solid, iron sulfide outer core layer, a deeper liquid
              core layer, and a solid inner core. The planet's density is the
              second highest in the Solar System at 5.427 g/cm3 , only slightly
              less than Earth's density.
            </p>
            <!-- PARAGRAPH SURFACE -->
            <p
              id="paragraphSurface"
              class="font-League-Spartan hidden w-[20.4375rem] text-sm font-normal leading-[1.375rem] text-[#fff] md:w-[21.1875rem] xl:w-[21.875rem] xl:text-sm xl:leading-[1.5625rem]"
            >
              Mercury's surface is similar in appearance to that of the Moon,
              showing extensive mare-like plains and heavy cratering, indicating
              that it has been geologically inactive for billions of years. It
              is more heterogeneous than either Mars's or the Moonâ€™s.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- SOURCE LINK WKIPEDIA -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-1">
            <h3
              class="font-League-Spartan text-xs font-normal leading-[1.5625rem] text-[#fff] opacity-50 xl:text-sm"
            >
              Source :
            </h3>
            <a
              id="wikipediaOverview"
              href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercury_(planet)"
              class="font-League-Spartan flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold leading-[1.5625rem] text-[#fff] underline opacity-50 xl:text-sm"
            >
              Wikipedia
              <img src="/images/icon-source.svg" alt="arrow" class="" />
            </a>
            <a
              id="wikipediaInternal"
              href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercury_(planet)#Internal_structure"
              class="font-League-Spartan flex hidden cursor-pointer items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold leading-[1.5625rem] text-[#fff] underline opacity-50 xl:text-sm"
            >
              Wikipedia
              <img src="/images/icon-source.svg" alt="arrow" class="" />
            </a>
            <a
              id="wikipediaSurface"
              href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercury_(planet)#Surface_geology"
              class="font-League-Spartan flex hidden cursor-pointer items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold leading-[1.5625rem] text-[#fff] underline opacity-50 xl:text-sm"
            >
              Wikipedia
              <img src="/images/icon-source.svg" alt="arrow" class="" />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- OVERVIEW , STRUCTURE & SURFACE FOR TABLET & DESKTOP-->
        <div
          class="hidden md:flex-col md:gap-4 md:max-2xl:flex xl:mt-[2.44rem]"
        >
          <!-- OVERVIEW -->
          <button
            type="button"
            class="overViewBtn flex h-10 w-[17.5625rem] items-start border border-solid border-[#fff] border-opacity-20 pb-[0.44rem] pl-5 pt-2 text-[0.5625rem] font-bold uppercase leading-[1.5625rem] tracking-[0.12056rem] text-[#fff] active:border-none active:bg-[#419EBB] xl:max-h-14 xl:w-[21.875rem] xl:pb-[0.69rem] xl:pl-7 xl:pt-3 xl:text-xs xl:tracking-[0.16069rem]"
          >
            <span class="mr-[0.88rem] opacity-50 xl:mr-7">01</span> OVERVIEW
          </button>
          <!-- Internal Structure -->
          <button
            type="button"
            class="structureBtn flex h-10 w-[17.5625rem] items-start border border-solid border-[#fff] border-opacity-20 pb-[0.44rem] pl-5 pt-2 text-[0.5625rem] font-bold uppercase leading-[1.5625rem] tracking-[0.12056rem] text-[#fff] active:border-none active:bg-[#419EBB] xl:max-h-14 xl:w-[21.875rem] xl:pb-[0.69rem] xl:pl-7 xl:pt-3 xl:text-xs xl:tracking-[0.16069rem]"
          >
            <span class="mr-[0.88rem] opacity-50 xl:mr-7">02</span> Internal Structure
          </button>
          <!-- Surface Geology -->
          <button
            type="button"
            class="surfaceBtn flex h-10 w-[17.5625rem] items-start border border-solid border-[#fff] border-opacity-20 pb-[0.44rem] pl-5 pt-2 text-[0.5625rem] font-bold uppercase leading-[1.5625rem] tracking-[0.12056rem] text-[#fff] active:border-none active:bg-[#419EBB] xl:max-h-14 xl:w-[21.875rem] xl:pb-[0.69rem] xl:pl-7 xl:pt-3 xl:text-xs xl:tracking-[0.16069rem]"
          >
            <span class="mr-[0.88rem] opacity-50 xl:mr-7">03</span> Surface Geology
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- PLANET DATA -->
    <section
      class="mx-6 mb-[2.94rem] mt-7 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 md:mb-[2.25rem] md:ml-[2.44rem] md:mr-10 md:mt-[1.69rem] md:gap-[0.69rem] md:max-2xl:flex-row md:max-2xl:justify-between xl:mx-[10.31rem] xl:mb-14 xl:mt-[5.44rem] xl:gap-[1.87rem]"
    >
      <!-- ROTATION TIME -->
      <div
        class="flex h-12 w-[20.4375rem] items-center justify-between border border-solid border-[#fff] border-opacity-20 px-6 py-[0.56rem] md:h-[5.5rem] md:w-[10.25rem] md:gap-[0.38rem] md:pb-[1.19rem] md:pl-[0.94rem] md:pt-4 md:max-2xl:flex-col md:max-2xl:items-start xl:h-32 xl:w-[15.9375rem] xl:gap-1 xl:pb-[1.69rem] xl:pl-[1.44rem] xl:pt-5"
      >
        <h3
          class="font-League Spartan text-[0.5rem] uppercase leading-4 tracking-[0.04544rem] text-[#fff] opacity-50 xl:text-[0.6875rem] xl:tracking-[0.0625rem]"
        >
          ROTATION TIME
        </h3>
        <h3
          class="font-Antonio text-xl font-normal uppercase leading-normal tracking-[-0.04688rem] text-[#fff] md:text-2xl md:tracking-[-0.05625rem] xl:text-[2.5rem] xl:tracking-[-0.09375rem]"
        >
          58.6 days
        </h3>
      </div>
      <!-- REVOLUTION TIME -->
      <div
        class="flex h-12 w-[20.4375rem] items-center justify-between border border-solid border-[#fff] border-opacity-20 px-6 py-[0.56rem] md:h-[5.5rem] md:w-[10.25rem] md:gap-[0.38rem] md:pb-[1.19rem] md:pl-[0.94rem] md:pt-4 md:max-2xl:flex-col md:max-2xl:items-start xl:h-32 xl:w-[15.9375rem] xl:gap-1 xl:pb-[1.69rem] xl:pl-[1.44rem] xl:pt-5"
      >
        <h3
          class="font-League Spartan text-[0.5rem] uppercase leading-4 tracking-[0.04544rem] text-[#fff] opacity-50 xl:text-[0.6875rem] xl:tracking-[0.0625rem]"
        >
          REVOLUTION TIME
        </h3>
        <h3
          class="font-Antonio text-xl font-normal uppercase leading-normal tracking-[-0.04688rem] text-[#fff] md:text-2xl md:tracking-[-0.05625rem] xl:text-[2.5rem] xl:tracking-[-0.09375rem]"
        >
          87.97 days
        </h3>
      </div>
      <!-- radius -->
      <div
        class="flex h-12 w-[20.4375rem] items-center justify-between border border-solid border-[#fff] border-opacity-20 px-6 py-[0.56rem] md:h-[5.5rem] md:w-[10.25rem] md:gap-[0.38rem] md:pb-[1.19rem] md:pl-[0.94rem] md:pt-4 md:max-2xl:flex-col md:max-2xl:items-start xl:h-32 xl:w-[15.9375rem] xl:gap-1 xl:pb-[1.69rem] xl:pl-[1.44rem] xl:pt-5"
      >
        <h3
          class="font-League Spartan text-[0.5rem] uppercase leading-4 tracking-[0.04544rem] text-[#fff] opacity-50 xl:text-[0.6875rem] xl:tracking-[0.0625rem]"
        >
          radius
        </h3>
        <h3
          class="font-Antonio text-xl font-normal uppercase leading-normal tracking-[-0.04688rem] text-[#fff] md:text-2xl md:tracking-[-0.05625rem] xl:text-[2.5rem] xl:tracking-[-0.09375rem]"
        >
          2,439.7 km
        </h3>
      </div>
      <!-- AVERAGE TEMP. -->
      <div
        class="flex h-12 w-[20.4375rem] items-center justify-between border border-solid border-[#fff] border-opacity-20 px-6 py-[0.56rem] md:h-[5.5rem] md:w-[10.25rem] md:gap-[0.38rem] md:pb-[1.19rem] md:pl-[0.94rem] md:pt-4 md:max-2xl:flex-col md:max-2xl:items-start xl:h-32 xl:w-[15.9375rem] xl:gap-1 xl:pb-[1.69rem] xl:pl-[1.44rem] xl:pt-5"
      >
        <h3
          class="font-League Spartan text-[0.5rem] uppercase leading-4 tracking-[0.04544rem] text-[#fff] opacity-50 xl:text-[0.6875rem] xl:tracking-[0.0625rem]"
        >
          AVERAGE TEMP.
        </h3>
        <h3
          class="font-Antonio text-xl font-normal uppercase leading-normal tracking-[-0.04688rem] text-[#fff] md:text-2xl md:tracking-[-0.05625rem] xl:text-[2.5rem] xl:tracking-[-0.09375rem]"
        >
          430Â°c
        </h3>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style></style>
</Layout>

<script is:inline>
  // BUTTONS
  const overViewBtn = document.querySelectorAll(".overViewBtn");
  const structureBtn = document.querySelectorAll(".structureBtn");
  const surfaceBtn = document.querySelectorAll(".surfaceBtn");
  // IMAGES
  const internal = document.querySelectorAll("#internal");
  const geology = document.querySelectorAll("#geology");
  const overview = document.querySelector("#overview");
  // WIKIPEDIA
  const wikipediaOverview = document.querySelector("#wikipediaOverview");
  const wikipediaInternal = document.querySelector("#wikipediaInternal");
  const wikipediaSurface = document.querySelector("#wikipediaSurface");
  // PARAGRAPH
  const paragraphOverview = document.querySelector("#paragraphOverview");
  const paragraphInternal = document.querySelector("#paragraphInternal");
  const paragraphSurface = document.querySelector("#paragraphSurface");

  //  FUNCTIONS

  structureBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
    overview.classList.add("hidden");
    internal.classList.remove("hidden");
  });
</script>
